CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 20, 1960, pg. B10 reads: "Chi Delta Mu Fraternity Entertains Lavishly - Dr. Charles Cephas, far right, and guests; Mrs. Cephas fourth from right." Portion of accompanying article published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 20, 1960, pg. A7 by Toki Schalk Johnson reads:"Wednesday brought forth the annual dinner dance given by the Chi Delta Mu Fraternity in beautifully decorated New Arena."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of five men, including Dr. Charles Cephas, far right, and five women, including Mrs. Charles Cephas, fourth from right, seated at rectangular banquet table for Chi Delta Mu dinner dance in New Arena Supper Club
